metadataAttributes.Title: Introduction to Data Science
metadataAttributes.Short Intro: Learn one of the most battle-tested, internationally-recognized processes for solving data-science problems. Upon completing this course, you’ll have a reliable system for tackling data challenges, as well as the skills & know-how to share your findings with the world.
metadataAttributes.Skills: Predictive Analytics, Exploratory Data Analysis, Data Storytelling, CRISP-DM, Blog Posts, GitHub Portfolios, AI Algorithms in Python, Statistical Modeling Fundamentals
